{"type": "article", "id": 32463, "title": "这些花瓶，你真以为是竹子编的？｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-09-21T23:07:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 33020, "name": "Roumelight"}, {"id": 15495, "name": "Floyd"}, {"id": 21916, "name": "Vinaya"}, {"id": 33021, "name": "SSTEEL"}, {"id": 33022, "name": "Hélène Morbu"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 92, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160921230128WIL4cSjDt2PZ71m0.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Quetzal &amp; Codex by Hélène Morbu</h3><p>在巴黎家居装饰博览会秋展上，法国陶瓷艺术家 <a href=\"http://www.morbu.fr/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Hélène Morbu</a> 带来了两组让人大开眼界的花瓶。远远看去，你或许会因为独特的表面将它们错认为是织物或是竹编的装饰品。Morbu 采用了一种特别的塑造技巧，利用梳子将陶土缓慢细致地反复挤压，最终制作出了 Quetzal 系列富有编织感的表面。另一组采用砂岩制作的 Codex 花瓶采用了相同的工艺，多孔表面就像是鼓起的渔网，仿佛被赋予了“弹性”。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609212304113s5whcZoKOgM0TiE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.679707\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921230411O65ml7V1KxuoBJP0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.738386\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921230411As8kVCN4BU3uzcSL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609212304110zGhwmX7AHEjfMno.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.539120\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921230412VqohtQCJe81LuBgS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.262836\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Altruis by Vinaya</h3><p>还记得我们曾经介绍过的一款能够监视情绪的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/28319.html\">智能手环</a>吗？它背后的设计团队 <a href=\"http://www.vinaya.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Vinaya</a> 最近推出了一套名为 Altruis 的智能首饰，其中包括分为金银两种颜色的戒指、手镯和项链。这些首饰都内置了蓝牙功能，用户可以根据自己的需求通过配套的应用（目前只有 <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/nz/app/altruis/id1049449263?mt=8\" rel=\"nofollow\">iOS</a> 版）定制个性化的情景模式，将手机上一些不重要的提醒设置静音，同时可以设置首饰在接到某些重要信息时产生振动，从而减轻对手机的过度依赖。Altruis 系列通过 USB 电缆进行充电，待机时间长达一个多月。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921230351Og7bH9E0IuKUxzWl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921230351tiC58KQylJDH6vZL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921230352yDQHBRngX9r4w7le.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609212303520bIYDyTjHS6nm2Zi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.733496\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921230353SUM3B8zxnqbVJuWy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921230351AeDtTxsEWKcPG30N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>VISTA Lounge chair by SSTEEL</h3><p>在 2016 泰国家具展上，金属家具品牌 <a href=\"http://www.ssteeldesign.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">SSTEEL</a> 展出了这张名为 <a href=\"http://www.ssteeldesign.com/portfolio-item/vista/\" rel=\"nofollow\">VISTA</a> 的休闲椅。座位和椅背像是外部简洁框架的延伸，微妙的弧度给人一种仿佛黑色布料悬在空中的飘逸感，和不锈钢本身坚硬稳固的特性形成了有趣的对比，相当抢眼。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609212303322xIX7tdFRCi5yPu9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609212303328ShIksMYFq6DlO7B.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921230332boU92MhDFqJKZj5c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609212303335tQUKovrn04FmaV3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921230333VJ6YKGrwuziL9PIg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609212303329UFA0iB1ZXSazhDP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Bookshelf Lightbridge by Roumelight</h3><p>希腊灯具制造商 <a href=\"http://roumelight.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Roumelight</a> 以闻名遐迩的旧金山金门大桥和希腊的里翁-安提里翁大桥（Rio Antirio）为灵感设计了这款名为 <a href=\"http://roumelight.com/work/bookshelf-lightbridge\" rel=\"nofollow\">Lightbridge</a> 的书架。书架上层装有两种完全不同的灯具，温暖的白光和昏暗的红光营造出一股独特的气氛，有着很强的装饰性。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921230304o51tbHLuSeDj9CqX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.598291\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921230304uFxQYjSLNIBWvw6e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921230304y6UXWS0FLrVwzhH9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.132503\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921230305GrhSKgQxA5ti9u7X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.298701\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921230305YsJGeyPEzIAnDvFc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Coat Rack by Floyd</h3><p>来自美国底特律的家具品牌 <a href=\"https://floyddetroit.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Floyd</a> 创立于 2013 年，旗下的产品都是围绕着城市生活所打造的，换言之就是组装、搬运起来容易而且耐用的家具。这张看起来像是一个人斜倚着墙的衣架同样遵循了这一设计理念，由分段的长木钉和用来连接的金属管构成，整个结构看上去稳固简洁，组装起来也并不复杂。除了衣物之外，你还可以把它当作一个灯具支架，改造成一个落地灯放在屋内也很耐看。这是它的<a href=\"https://floyddetroit.com/products/the-floyd-coat-rack?taxon_id=6#\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 145 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921230231sqKwI36lzh4mMLeS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921230232RCWfDa5TbHF3zl8i.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921230232h0OBm94LKage7fxv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921230233O45oEdz7vR1NwWLg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921230232w0hO9SGnJd6ufezi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921230233SQzdgqx2wRGF8hOY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.463542\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>CS by Angelina Pischikova</h3><p>白俄罗斯设计师 Angelina Pischikova 受该国最大的电气公司 <a href=\"http://crazyservice.by/\" rel=\"nofollow\">CS</a> 的委托，设计了一套名片和灯泡包装。Pischikova 在翻阅旧物理书时得到启发，选择和公司密切相关的电路图作为名片的主要元素。鉴于爱迪生将萤火虫描述为理想的冷光光源，Pischikova 决定延续这种与自然间的联系。她根据灯泡的款式让画师 Anna Orlovskaya 绘制了若干种昆虫的图案，巧妙地和包装正面的镂空部分结合在了一起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921230145s0GXM9O7gKWuIxdY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666429\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921230150WKujsQGDA6Tw5Jkx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921230152xPl5IRmg2EfrHDNM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921230150n5hb4Vmel7r20sjY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707143\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921230149VzPvgnyAeofOQuMl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921230150iyVLaIzrGeEJTmj3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}